b) Chain AE color stuns to lock em down and pick em off. Can't say enough about this at your level, and for another 15 levels probably.<br>
c) Get good with clicking your intended targets; foot-area clicks can work better than torso or head clicks. Stay sharp and pay attention to mob HP bars, and the flashing mob name when targetted.<br>
<br>
Aug to conserve mana if you find yourself low a lot, alacrity when you can spare it, despite the short duration; things dying faster is always good. Tanks with and without a haste item can have differing preferences, as well. Low stamina stat fighters nay want aug for the stamina benefits.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://forums.castersrealm.com/cgi-bin/eq/ultimatebb.cgi?category=5">Enchanter Forums</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
